                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">policeman, E</hi> 33). I produce a certificate of Handley's</p>
               <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="184912170061"></xptr>
               <p>conviction—(<hi rend="italic">read—Convicted May</hi>, 1848, <hi rend="italic">of stealing</hi> 20 <hi rend="italic">yards of printed cotton, confined three months</hi>)—I am quite sure she is the person.</p>
